snippet.title: The Tenth Line - A Few (More) Minutes of Gameplay
snippet.description:
More up-to-date gameplay footage of The Tenth Line, an upcoming indie RPG! Demonstrates some exploration, a battle, some leveling up, and a game of cards.

The Tenth Line is coming to Steam on March 17th, 2017, and to consoles later this spring.
